snippet.title: Air Guitar Warrior - Soundtrack Medley
snippet.description:
Listen to 9 of the 19 custom tracks in the upcoming Air Guitar Warrior game, out now on Xbox One. Music by the amazingly talented Mr. Fastfinger (https://www.youtube.com/user/MrFastfingerNet) and Samppa Siurala (www.facebook.com/humantricksmusic/)!
http://airguitarwarrior.com
